metadata.name: Down To FUD
metadata.description: Though a some-what dysfunctional way of creating community, owning this NFT does exactly that! Down To FUD is a simple yet effective way to meet like minded Degens that are not afraid to call out scammers on their BS! It doubles cleverly as a way for Legit Degens to identify what projects others are in as well as a dating tool! Do you have a spicy little Twitter connection you want to FUD hard? Not sure if they are DTF? Simply check their wallet for a token. If they have one, you know they are DTF! Down To FUD is a collection of 1,155 ERC-1155 NFT's that can be burnt to redeem on a 1 of 1 basis ***for all future collections***.
